lead_paragraph: Chelsea midfielder Nemanja Matic hopes a late season flourish can make amends for the champions' dreadful start to the current campaign and put them in contention to break into the Premier League's top four for Champions League spots.

headline.print_headline: Chelsea's Matic Yet to Give Up on Top Four Finish
